We also have experience with anonymisation tools such as Microsoft Presidio and custom NER models, which can be applied to ensure that no personal data is used in AI training pipelines, aligning with our known compliance constraint of restricting personal data in training pipelines.

Our access control standards include multi-factor authentication, role-based access control design experience, and privileged access management solutions like CyberArk Conjur and HashiCorp Vault. These measures can help prevent unauthorized access to data.

